throw off; {#srajamapi SirasyaMDaH kziptAM#} 
{#DunotyahiSaMkayA#} <ls>Ś. 7. 24.</ls>

{@--4@} To kindle, excite,
fan (as fire); {#vAyunA DUyamAno hi vanaM#}
{#dahati pAvakaH#} <ls>Mb.</ls>; {#pavanaDUtaH…agniH#}  
